{"tid":658851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加州選美皇后中風後面癱 做手術有望重現笑顏","createTime":"2018-05-09T10:28:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T11:06:01.000Z","uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f7c0377357d7745c187e94a525b4124dce073243","tid":658851,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T10:28:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180508/_2018050817404081529_detail.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180508%2F_2018050817404081529_detail.jpg&h=b90f5bff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">曾在選美獲獎的Julia,因中風致面癱。網圖</span><br />\n<br />\n人生充滿坎坷起伏，沒有幾多人一生人能夠順風順水。來自美國的女生Julia Hernandez就深刻體會到這點，她曾經是加州的選美皇后，但不幸的是，她5年前因中風，導致臉部部分癱瘓，變成「歪嘴」。<br />\nJulia曾擁有令無數女人艷羨的美貌，但在2013年時，當時年僅20歲的她突然嚴重中風，腦內有血細胞破裂，導致她臉部右側癱瘓，再也無法正常微笑，甚至不能正常的享用美食。<br />\n剛患病時，Julia難以接受現實，她不敢照鏡子，不敢出門見人，「我的世界崩塌了，覺得我再也不是以前的自己了」。<br />\n而在家人的鼓勵和開導下，Julia慢慢地恢復了信心，意識到美貌只是一個人的表層。她重返校園獲得學士學位，漸變成一位有自信的女孩。<br />\n到今年5月，Julia終於找到一家能夠進行面部重建的醫院。經過8個小時手術，醫生成功在Julia臉部植入了部分大腿肌肉，使她有望重拾正常笑容。預計Julia需要約一年時間才恢復，但她表示已急不及待想要看手術成果。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180508/_2018050817404128762_detail.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180508%2F_2018050817404128762_detail.jpg&h=8787199e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180508/_2018050817404145572_detail.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180508%2F_2018050817404145572_detail.jpg&h=93a4dc30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/710578-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E5%8A%A0%E5%B7%9E%E9%81%B8%E7%BE%8E%E7%9A%87%E5%90%8E%E4%B8%AD%E9%A2%A8%E5%BE%8C%E9%9D%A2%E7%99%B1+%E5%81%9A%E6%89%8B%E8%A1%93%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%9B%E9%87%8D%E7%8F%BE%E7%AC%91%E9%A1%8F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F710578-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%25B7%259E%25E9%2581%25B8%25E7%25BE%258E%25E7%259A%2587%25E5%2590%258E%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E5%25BE%258C%25E9%259D%25A2%25E7%2599%25B1%2B%25E5%2581%259A%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%25A1%2593%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%259C%259B%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%258F%25BE%25E7%25AC%2591%25E9%25A1%258F&d=phDuAanM8StDKKQ8E6Zu5P7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=e2596f04\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F710578-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%25B7%259E%25E9%2581%25B8%25E7%25BE%258E%25E7%259A%2587%25E5%2590%258E%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E5%25BE%258C%25E9%259D%25A2%25E7%2599%25B1%2B%25E5%2581%259A%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%25A1%2593%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%259C%259B%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%258F%25BE%25E7%25AC%2591%25E9%25A1%258F&h=9aa480a2\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/710578-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E5%8A%A0%E5%B7%9E%E9%81%B8%E7%BE%8E%E7%9A%87%E5%90%8E%E4%B8%AD%E9%A2%A8%E5%BE%8C%E9%9D%A2%E7%99%B1+%E5%81%9A%E6%89%8B%E8%A1%93%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%9B%E9%87%8D%E7%8F%BE%E7%AC%91%E9%A1%8F</a>"},{"pid":"7911dd13087bfa53f74aabc64ee3d9ae930b197e","tid":658851,"uid":50022,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T10:31:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bdcf7ebd1f2bc03d557552ce6f8f8a3bcc2be1d","tid":658851,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7911dd13087bfa53f74aabc64ee3d9ae930b197e","tid":658851,"uid":50022,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T10:31:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T10:32:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"h